Dependency Information

Apache Maven

<dependency>
  <groupId>io.dropwizard</groupId>
  <artifactId>dropwizard-parent</artifactId>
  <version>1.2.2</version>
  <type>pom</type>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'io.dropwizard:dropwizard-parent:pom:1.2.2'

Apache Ivy

<dependency org="io.dropwizard" name="dropwizard-parent" rev="1.2.2">
  <artifact name="dropwizard-parent" type="pom" />
</dependency>

Groovy Grape

@Grapes(
@Grab(group='io.dropwizard', module='dropwizard-parent', version='1.2.2')
)

Gradle/Grails

compile 'io.dropwizard:dropwizard-parent:1.2.2'

Scala SBT

libraryDependencies += "io.dropwizard" % "dropwizard-parent" % "1.2.2"

Leiningen
